# Header Component Rules

## Overview
Rules and patterns for the Header component (`src/components/organisms/Header.tsx`)

## Purpose
Main site header with logo and navigation, including brand accent elements

## Rules

### Core Requirements
- ✅ **Layout Structure:** Use consistent container pattern (`max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4`)
- ✅ **Component Composition:** Compose using Logo and NavBar molecules
- ✅ **Branding Elements:** Include brand color accent bar (`h-2 bg-[#8a0028]`)
- ✅ **Border Design:** Top border using brand color (`border-b border-[#8a0028]`)
- ✅ **Flex Layout:** `flex items-center justify-between` for logo and nav positioning
- ✅ **Responsive Spacing:** Consistent padding and margins
- ✅ **Semantic HTML:** Use proper `<header>` element

## Code Template
```typescript
import Logo from "@/components/atoms/Logo";
import NavBar from "@/components/molecules/NavBar";

export function Header() {
  return (
    <header className="w-full border-b border-[#8a0028]">
      <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
        <Logo />
        <NavBar />
      </div>
      <div className="h-2 bg-[#8a0028]"></div>
    </header>
  );
}

export default Header;
```

## Implementation Details

### Component Composition
- Logo: Brand logo with navigation capability
- NavBar: Navigation menu with multiple links
- No additional props required

### Styling Classes
- Header: `w-full border-b border-[#8a0028]`
- Container: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex items-center justify-between`
- Accent bar: `h-2 bg-[#8a0028]`

### Layout Structure
- Full width header with brand color border
- Constrained content container with centered max-width
- Logo on left, navigation on right
- Brand color accent bar at bottom

## Layout Specifications

### Container System
- Max width: `max-w-7xl` (1280px)
- Centering: `mx-auto`
- Horizontal padding: `px-4` (16px)
- Vertical padding: `py-4` (16px)

### Flexbox Layout
- Direction: Row (default)
- Alignment: `items-center` (vertical center)
- Justification: `justify-between` (space between logo and nav)

### Brand Elements
- Top border: Brand color (`border-[#8a0028]`)
- Accent bar: 8px height, brand color background
- Full width coverage

## Visual Hierarchy

### Branding
- Logo positioned prominently on the left
- Navigation accessible on the right
- Brand color used consistently throughout

### Spacing
- Consistent 16px padding on all sides
- 32px vertical spacing for accent bar
- Proper spacing between logo and navigation

